originalSql:
SELECT 
    t.title AS movie_title,
    a.name AS actor_name,
    r.role AS actor_role,
    c.note AS cast_note,
    ti.info AS movie_info
FROM 
    title t
JOIN 
    movie_companies mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id
JOIN 
    company_name cn ON mc.company_id = cn.id
JOIN 
    cast_info c ON t.id = c.movie_id
JOIN 
    aka_name a ON c.person_id = a.person_id
JOIN 
    role_type r ON c.role_id = r.id
LEFT JOIN 
    movie_info ti ON t.id = ti.movie_id
WHERE 
    cn.country_code = 'USA'
ORDER BY 
    t.production_year DESC, 
    a.name

INNER JOIN ("movie_info" RIGHT JOIN ("title" INNER JOIN ("movie_companies" INNER JOIN (SELECT *
FROM "company_name"
WHERE "country_code" = 'USA') AS "t0" ON "movie_companies"."company_id" = "t0"."id") ON "title"."id" = "movie_companies"."movie_id") ON "movie_info"."movie_id" = "title"."id") ON "cast_info"."movie_id" = "title"."id"
INNER JOIN "aka_name" ON "cast_info"."person_id" = "aka_name"."person_id"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "cast_info"."role_id" = "s1"."id"
ORDER BY "title"."production_year" DESC NULLS FIRST, "aka_name"."name") AS "t2"
